1. Functional requirements
System shall display the list of products
System shall allow users to buy products
System shall allow users search products
System shall allow users to add products to cart
System shall store users' personal information and card information
System shall integrate with credit card service
System shall allow users to write products reviews
System shall allow staffs to manage products
System shall allow staffs to generate reports
System shall integrate with the existing order application
2. Non-functional requirements
Shopping cart shall be friendly
UI shall be friendly
System shall be Secured
System shall be scalable
System shall be cost-efficiency
System shall have a good performance